                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 13.916,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 84365,
                                "text": "Mr. Justice Douglas will also announce the judgment -- opinion of the Court in 73-1231 and 1234, Linden Lumber Division against the Labor Board and the related case."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 13.916,
